revision.text: Possibly: Tou en hagiois patros hēmōn Iōannou Archiepiskopou Kōnstantinoupoleōs tou Chrysostomou tōn heuriskomenōn tomos prōtos [-ogdoos], di epimeleias k[a]i analōmatōn Herrikou tou Sabiliou en palaiōn antigraphōn ekdotheis. By St. John Chrysostom. (Etonae : In Collegio Regali, excudebat Ioannes Norton, in Graecis &c., Regius typographus, Anno M.DC.XII [1611-1613]) http://library.st-andrews.ac.uk/record=b1689048~S1
